Package: HMMSSFGenerativeRepair
Title: Generative Validation and Repair Diagnostics for HMM-SSF Models
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        given = "Aurelien",
        family = "Nicosia",
        role = c("aut", "cre"),
        email = "116816597+AurelienNicosiaULaval@users.noreply.github.com"
    )
Description: Provides simulation, compatibility, sharpness, and interpretation
    diagnostics for hidden Markov step-selection models. The package is a
    development scaffold for extending gmov-style generative validation to
    HMM-SSF and HMM-iSSA models while keeping latent-chain, state-kernel, and
    state-decoding uncertainty diagnostics separate.
URL: https://github.com/AurelienNicosiaULaval/HMMSSFGenerativeRepair,
    https://aureliennicosiaulaval.github.io/HMMSSFGenerativeRepair/
BugReports: https://github.com/AurelienNicosiaULaval/HMMSSFGenerativeRepair/issues
